headline: Domino's Pizza Is Now A Fresh Buy After The Recent Dip (Rating Upgrade)
summary: Domino's Pizza shows 7% sales growth, 1.74% yield, and improved margins with a 23.66x P/E below historical averages. Read why DPZ stock is upgraded to buy.
